  <div class="callout" style="margin-top:20px">
    <p><strong>Shortcuts:</strong> Skip the menu by prefixing your message &mdash; <code>search:</code>, <code>review:</code>, <code>overview:</code>, <code>deep:</code>, <code>research:</code>, <code>news:</code>, <code>catchup:</code>, <code>list</code>, <code>--end</code>. Deep Search (multi-round iterative) is available via the <code>deepsearch:</code> prefix.</p>
