      <tr><td><span class="badge badge-green">Review / Analysis</span></td><td>Codex gpt-5.2 / gpt-5.3-codex-spark</td><td>Code review, corpus analysis, enrichment, fact-checking, and link verification. Spark used for verification and enrichment tasks.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="badge badge-amber">Startup</span></td><td>Claude Haiku</td><td>Lightweight data-gathering subagents during /start Phase 2 only</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </RefTable>
